Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.19,0:24:30.15,TitleEP,en,0,0,235,,Giant Toad Magic
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.19,0:24:30.15,TitleEP,en,0,0,90,,Jiraiyan
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.19,0:24:30.15,NoteOnAnime,en,0,60,30,,{\an3\fs32}Look forwards for it!